#
# File Browser Frescobaldi extension
#

extension-name: File Browser
short-description: Panel with file browser for navigating directories
description: <
  This extension provides a panel with a file browser.
  Initially the panel shows an 'Open Folder' button.
  Selecting a folder displays its contents as a tree of folders and files.
  Double-clicking a file opens it in the editor.
  >
version: 1.0.0
api-version: 0.9.0
maintainers: [
  Claude Code <noreply@anthropic.com>
  ]
license: GPL3
website: https://github.com/frescobaldi-extensions/file-browser
repository: https://github.com/frescobaldi-extensions/file-browser.git
